title: Phosphor Icons for R
text: Create icon ph() function:  ’s 5 weights available:      Colorize icon using fill argument:  ’s two type icons: SVG icons, created ph() Font icons, created ph_i() ’s big debate Web Fonts vs SVG icons, mainly: Web fonts require htmlDependency include icons even use one, increase size document self contained mode. SVG icons won’t currently work shiny functions icon argument.
code: library(phosphoricons) ph("lightning") ph("lightning", weight = "thin") ph("lightning", weight = "light") ph("lightning", weight = "regular") ph("lightning", weight = "bold") ph("lightning", weight = "fill") ph("lightning", weight = "bold", fill = "gold")

title: Phosphor Icons for R
text: Fill icon according percentage:   Icon waffle:
code: ph_fill(   ph("heart", weight = "fill", height = 128),   colors = c("#DF0101", "#F6CECE"),   breaks = 0.7 ) ph_fill(   ph("star", weight = "fill", height = 128, stroke = "gold", `stroke-width` = 10),   colors = c("gold", "#FFF"),   breaks = 0.5,   orientation = "h" ) waffle_icon(   values = sample(c("Cats", "Dogs"), 200, TRUE),   colors = list(     Cats = "#456990",     Dogs = "#F45B69"   ),   icons = list(     Cats = ph("cat", height = NULL),     Dogs = ph("dog", height = NULL)   ),   ncol = 15,   nrow = 8,   width = "500px" )

title: Phosphor SVG Icons — ph
text: Create <svg></svg> tag render icon.

title: Phosphor SVG Icons — ph
code: ph(   name,   weight = c("light", "regular", "thin", "bold", "fill"),   fill = "currentColor",   rotate = NULL,   height = "1.33em",   width = NULL,   vertical_align = "-0.25em",   title = name,   ... )

title: Phosphor SVG Icons — ph
text: name Name icon use. weight Weight icon (thinnest thickest): thin, light (default), regular, bold fill. fill Fill color icon, default currentColor match color text icon used. rotate Numeric, angle rotate icon. height, width Height width valid CSS unit. vertical_align Vertical alignment icon, depend size icon. title Add <title> tag provides accessible, short-text description icon. Use NULL title. ... Attributes passed SVG tag.
